                                                                                                                                    services; procedures addressing idenﬁcaon and authencaon; system design
                                                                                                                                    documentaon; system conﬁguraon sengs and associated documentaon;
                                                                                                                                    system audit records; list of system accounts and services requiring single sign-on
                                                                                                                                    capability; other relevant documents or records].

